fulltitle: Carmen Lundy Presents Living The Jazzlife with Rhonda Hamilton: Episode 3 - Marvin "Smitty" Smith
description: Presented by Carmen Lundy and Afrasia Productions.  On "Living The Jazzlife with Rhonda Hamilton", Rhonda speaks to veteran jazz artists who share wit and wisdom on becoming successful performers, recording artists, bandleaders, composers and educators over their lifetimes.
